These are Puzzles for 2x4 Level 9

.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-9-1::.
The people use 4 different means of transport: helicopter, subway, car, jet-ski
4 different pets are kept: ferret, guinea-pig, hamster, rat
1. the owner of the rat is not to the right of the owner of the ferret##8
2. the owner of the rat is on the right of the person driving the helicopter##1
3. the person driving the subway is on the left or right of the person driving the car##3
4. the person driving the jet-ski is somewhere to the right of the owner of the guinea-pig##5
5. the person driving the jet-ski is not to the left of the owner of the rat##8
6. the owner of the hamster is somewhere to the left of the person driving the subway##5
7. the person driving the subway is somewhere between the person driving the helicopter and the owner of the guinea-pig##7
8. the person driving the subway and the owner of the rat have the same parity positions##9
9. the person driving the car and the owner of the ferret have different parity positions##9

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |    2    |     3      |    4    |
| Nationality   | helicopter | subway | car     | jet-ski |
| Pet           | hamster   | rat     | guinea-pig | ferret  |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-9-2::.
The people have 4 different jobs:  pilot, dressmaker, paramedic, bartender
The people have 4 different hobbies: dancing, drawing, sudoku, traveling
1. the person who's hobby is dancing is on the far left or far right##3
2. the person who's hobby is traveling and the dressmaker have the same parity positions##9
3. the person who's hobby is drawing is not to the right of the person who's hobby is sudoku##8
4. the person who's hobby is dancing is not to the right of the bartender##8
5. the person who's hobby is dancing is somewhere to the left of the pilot##5
6. the pilot is somewhere to the right of the person who's hobby is drawing##5
7. the dressmaker is somewhere to the right of the pilot##5
8. the bartender is on the far left or far right##3

.:: Answer ::.
|            |    1    |    2    |      3      |     4     |
| Beverage   | bartender     | paramedic    | pilot | dressmaker    |
| Hobby      | dancing | drawing | sudoku      | traveling |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-9-3::.
The people's birthday is in 4 different months: march, july, august, february
There 4 different types of food: artichoke, avocado, mango, pumpkin
1. the person who's birthday is in august is somewhere to the left of the person eating mango##5
2. the person eating artichoke is somewhere to the right of the person who's birthday is in august##5
3. the person who's birthday is in july is on the left of the person who's birthday is in august##1
4. the person who's birthday is in july is on the far left##1
5. the person who's birthday is in march is on the right of the person who's birthday is in august##1
6. the person who's birthday is in august is on the left of the person eating artichoke##1
7. the person eating artichoke is not to the left of the person eating avocado##8
8. the person who's birthday is in july and the person eating avocado have the same parity positions##9

.:: Answer ::.
|            |    1    |    2    |     3     |   4   |
| Beverage   | july    | august   | march    | february  |
| Food       | avocado | pumpkin | artichoke | mango |

