.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-9-5::.
The people have 4 different hobbies: hiking, gardening, chess, woodworking
4 different pets are kept: cat, dog, hedgehog, pony
1. the person who's hobby is chess is not the owner of the hedgehog##6
2. the owner of the cat and the person who's hobby is hiking have different parity positions##9
3. the owner of the dog and the person who's hobby is gardening have different parity positions##9
4. the owner of the dog is somewhere to the left of the person who's hobby is chess##5
5. the owner of the cat is on the left of the person who's hobby is woodworking##1
6. the person who's hobby is gardening is not the owner of the dog##6
7. the person who's hobby is woodworking is somewhere to the left of the person who's hobby is gardening##5
8. the owner of the cat is on the right of the person who's hobby is hiking##1
9. the owner of the pony is not the person who's hobby is woodworking##6

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1   |    2    |    3     |     4     |
| Music-Genre   | hiking | chess | woodworking  | gardening |
| Pet           | dog   | cat     | hedgehog | pony      |

