2. the baccarat-smoker is on the left of the siglo-smoker##1
3. the indian is somewhere to the left of the siglo-smoker##5
4. the american and the baccarat-smoker have the same parity positions##9
5. the siglo-smoker and the american have different parity positions##9
6. the indian is not to the left of the blend-smoker##8
7. the thai is somewhere to the left of the blend-smoker##5
8. the bluemaster-smoker is not to the right of the thai##8

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |     2     |     3      |     4     |
| Movie-Genre   | bluemaster | blend | baccarat | siglo |
| Nationality   | thai        | indian    | american   | brazilian |

