2. the owner of the hamster is not to the right of the owner of the rabbit##8
3. the owner of the rabbit is on the right of the owner of the mouse##1
4. the person eating cucumber is on the left of the person eating cranberry##1
5. the person eating cranberry is not the owner of the fish##6
6. the person eating banana is somewhere to the right of the person eating cranberry##5
7. the person eating cucumber and the owner of the rabbit have the same parity positions##9

.:: Answer ::.
|         |      1      |     2     |     3      |    4    |
| Hobby   | cucumber | cranberry | tomato | banana |
| Pet     | hamster     | mouse     | rabbit     | fish    |

