.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-9-10::.
There 4 different types of food: broccoli, papaya, pepper, watermelon
There are 4 different favourite beverages: hot-chocolate, tea, soy-milk, sprite
1. the person drinking sprite is not to the left of the person eating broccoli##8
2. the person eating watermelon and the person drinking sprite have the same parity positions##9
3. the person drinking tea is somewhere to the right of the person drinking soy-milk##5
4. the person eating pepper is on the left or right of the person drinking tea##3
5. the person eating papaya is somewhere between the person drinking tea and the person drinking sprite##7
6. the person eating watermelon is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |   1    |     2      |   3    |     4      |
| Food        | pepper | broccoli   | papaya | watermelon |
| Transport   | soy-milk   | tea | hot-chocolate    | sprite      |

