.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-9-12::.
4 different games are played: bridge, mah-jongg, go, canasta
The people use 4 different means of transport: bike, helicopter, taxi, trike
1. the person playing bridge is on the right of the person playing go##1
2. the person playing go is not to the left of the person driving the trike##8
3. the person playing canasta and the person driving the helicopter have the same parity positions##9
4. the person driving the trike is the person playing canasta##1
5. the person playing bridge is somewhere to the right of the person driving the bike##5
6. the person driving the taxi is on the left of the person playing canasta##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |  1   |   2   |   3   |     4      |
| Music-Genre   | mah-jongg  | canasta  | go | bridge    |
| Transport     | taxi | trike | bike  | helicopter |

