.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-9-15::.
There 4 different types of food: mango, peach, potato, tomato
The people use 4 different means of transport: trike, tram, helicopter, van
1. the person eating peach and the person driving the van have the same parity positions##9
2. the person driving the van is not to the left of the person eating peach##8
3. the person eating mango is somewhere between the person driving the trike and the person driving the van##7
4. the person driving the van is somewhere between the person driving the helicopter and the person eating mango##7
5. the person driving the tram is not the person eating tomato##6
6. the person eating peach is on the right of the person eating mango##1
7. the person eating potato is in an even position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |   2   |   3   |    4    |
| Food          | tomato | mango | peach | potato  |
| Music-Genre   | trike    | tram | van | helicopter |

