 1. the chinese and the fan r&b have the same parity positions##9
 2. the indian is not to the right of the chinese##8
 3. the fan blues is somewhere between the chinese and the german##7
 4. the fan r&b is somewhere to the left of the indian##5
 5. the indian is in an odd position##4
 6. the fan r&b is not to the left of the italian##8
 7. the italian and the fan jazz have the same parity positions##9
 8. the italian is on the left or right of the fan soul##3
 9. the fan soul is in an odd position##4
10. the italian is not to the right of the fan blues##8

.:: Answer ::.
|               |  1   |    2    |   3   |    4     |
